Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:59.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}許せば進めるし　恨みは立ち止らす
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:04.08,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:09.20,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君をずっと立ち止める　その全てと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:14.92,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して　進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:24.36,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　と名付けても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:29.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生涯枯れることのない花　になることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:34.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}真面目に生きていれば　いつか報われる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうやって言い切ってしまえば　それは嘘になる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:44.69,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}身に起こるその数十％　自業自得でも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:49.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残りの数％　誰のせいでもないその不平等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:59.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}一番いけないことはさ　自分はダメだと思うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:04.68,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは僕のせいにしな　それも僕のせいにしてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:09.72,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕以外を許して進んで行きなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:15.29,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君自身のことも許してあげてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:59.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宽恕促人前行 仇恨让人停滞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:04.08,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:09.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅让你一直停滞不前之事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:14.92,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:24.36,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便取名为永不凋谢之花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:29.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也无法永不凋谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.01,0:04:34.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&HDA7B00&}认真活着就会有回报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此断言的话语必定是谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:44.69,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}百分之几十是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:49.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的百分之几不怨任何人 如此不公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:59.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\3c&H1200FF&\t(2560,2810,\3c&H265CF5&)\t(3269,3519,\3c&HDA7B00&)\t(3603,3811,\3c&H47C73E&)\t(3937,4103,\3c&H5F2558&)\t(4437,4562,\3c&H386A2D&)\t(5396,5438,\3c&H1200FF&)\t(6189,6481,\3c&H45B6FE&,\bord0.8)\t(8274,8441,\blur0,\3c&H103568&,\bord2,\1c&HCCE1F4&)\t(8775,9275,\3c&H52164B&)\t(9359,9609,\blur3,\3c&H103568&)}最糟糕的 是自我否定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:04.68,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把那个当成我的错吧 把这个也归咎于我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:09.72,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原谅除我以外的所有人 前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:15.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也原谅你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.29,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうじゃない　求めるものは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}強くこの手で掴もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}泣いたって変わらないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑っても同じ　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものが守れないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弱い僕のせい　そう思っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうして？　いま　ここに僕がいる理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.66,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰が解らなくてもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.30,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう　君がいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}見境無く燃える焔　 群衆が指をさす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.77,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}僕はきっと強くなって　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.69,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰だって守り抜く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.07,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}愛したいひとを想い　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:48.78,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&}闇をこの手で払おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.79,0:22:37.08,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是这样 追求之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:41.63,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要亲手去紧握
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:54.27,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一味哭泣 则无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.27,0:23:00.94,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}强颜欢笑也一样 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.57,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无法保护珍视之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.57,0:23:14.54,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为我太弱小 我如此想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:20.25,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？ 我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:23.66,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无人知晓也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.66,0:23:27.30,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要有你在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:34.06,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}燃尽万物的烈焰 饱受非议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:37.77,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定要变强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.69,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保护所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:44.07,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}心怀所爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.07,0:23:48.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HB54E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1}亲手驱散黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.78,0:23:50.78,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}站 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.18,0:00:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拜托你了 奥村
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望你能用降魔剑打倒不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.53,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我知道这是个无理又勉强的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是如果 如果你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能像你父亲那样对我施以些许慈悲之心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我想将希望寄托于你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢你看到最后 胜吕达摩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和我想的一样 真是不得了的内容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 虽然对不住胜吕同学的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.82,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥的火焰对不净王是否有效还只是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.02,0:00:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能因为这种不确切的事使用降魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 这封信是写给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.38,0:01:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐 你怎么能问他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.65,0:01:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我想帮他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.93,0:01:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 你知道自己现在的处境吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也被老头子救了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.55,0:01:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 如果我能派上用场 那我也想去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然 这只是我个人的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就要驳回你的请求…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}降临于此 回归于彼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.08,0:01:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐 你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还能做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他说要战斗 但不清楚他的状态我可没法批准
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在这里拔出来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}修拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥才刚刚放出火焰胡闹了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在把降魔剑给他太不理智了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是再发生点什么 肯定会被处刑的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我咏唱禁锢咒的时候梵蒂冈就已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们现在随时都可能以此为由处决他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在害怕也已经晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.12,0:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且这样没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果不净王复活 出现在了这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在它就比燐更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且你也见过那么多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他的火焰对目前为止遇到的恶魔都有效
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}值得一试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 你拔出来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拔不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.08,0:02:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知怎么回事 完全拔不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那我来帮你拔吧 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我自己拔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大概是哪里卡住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对 肯定是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐 你害怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过这也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚刚才因为掌握了火焰而欣喜若狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然而转瞬之间又回到了原点 你是这样的心情对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是再拔出这把剑 我会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也许又会发狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次说不定真的会伤到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你完全失去自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:24.55,biaoti,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fax-0.15\fad(0,518)\3c&HC4732D&\bord1.5\pos(1072,605)}气焰万丈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会因为这种事拔不出剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥哥 把剑还回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}晚上好 三位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}菲雷斯卿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梅菲斯特 你来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这问法还真是没礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我时隔已久的登场居然是在监狱里 我才失望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 亏我还是来给你们收拾烂摊子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fnArial}Das stärkste Gefängnis
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}防御力最高的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.54,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}梵蒂冈本部联系我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因方才咏唱禁锢咒之事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}经三贤者座下的审问委员会投票决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}处决奥村燐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}动作真快 这是真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都这种时候了 我可没这闲工夫跑过来撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雪男 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比起这些事情 讨伐不净王才是当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好意思 能帮我拿一下这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎么连这个都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然这么了解就来帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.67,0:06:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行的 我不擅长对付脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.99,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会过敏的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:06:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的鼻子已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王复活后会迅速成长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}待它完全成熟之时 京都将化为一座死城
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正带着蝮赶回外派所 马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请尽量让大家都到门口来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们那边能看见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能看见吗 蟒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就是不净王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讨伐不净王需要不少人手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然只是些简易的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就送给你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望这个能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 祝各位好运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之 我们先做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们应该也会被召集去讨伐不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}外派所让我们紧急集合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能动的人都去外派所
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么回事 外面好吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不是发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我听说抓住蝮了 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 柔造正带她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抓住蝮了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮 柔造
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.01,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢你把大家召集来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家 我是个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 还请大家听我说几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就在刚才 我和藤堂三郎太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.74,0:08:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用夺来的右眼和左眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}复活了不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王不是江户时代就被打倒了的恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}它一直以假死状态被封印在金刚深山的地下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在明陀宗座主胜吕达摩大人 正留在那里孤军奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.71,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请各位施以援手 打败不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真 真是任性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明明你自己把它复活的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再说了 不净王到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要怎么打倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在不是议论这些事的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驱魔队全体 巡逻一队和二队 以及深部一队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}出发讨伐不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不净王是腐之王的眷属
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全员接种疫苗以抵抗瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快去做接种疫苗的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蝮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}龙 龙士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的右眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请救救他 救救住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.83,0:10:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持 我带她去医务室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔造 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我稍后去和一队汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持请务必和驱魔塾的各位一起回旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}廉造 子猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给我好好保护少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是他出了什么事 你们就等死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好 交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快去救住持大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她可是女人啊 藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持 这也没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}柔哥都那样说了 我们就待在旅馆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾隐老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由于刚才放出了火焰 燐的处刑决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是梵蒂冈的决定 无法违抗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕同学 这个暂时给你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}俱利伽罗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有你父亲给燐的信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他说打倒不净王需要燐的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐是想帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们能把他救出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想让燐免除处刑 就只能让他将功赎罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.52,0:11:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把这些迷彩斗篷拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有隐身效果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应该能不被看守发现 接近他的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾隐队长 请快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是这样 说到底我也只是骑士团的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能擅自行动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}交给你们了 一切由你们自己判断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们去救燐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然很想去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但这样我们就是和梵蒂冈作对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但 但是如果就这样袖手旁观 再也见不到燐了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}牢房在这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕同学 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子猫 你在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三轮同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我必须保护少住持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且 我也一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么这样 你就这么怕柔哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:12:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么连出云都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.27,0:13:06.76,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别挡路廉造
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小鬼回旅馆睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我作为明陀的男人 死也要死得轰轰烈烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又是明陀又是后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的 麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你刚才说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有 是你说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我什么都没说啊 是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你少骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都怪子猫踩到我的脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原谅我吧 志摩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个斗篷虽然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是看不到对方也很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}应该就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是那扇门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本大爷是{\fnArial}Das stärkste Gefängnis {\r\blur2}防御力最高的牢房
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然我无法从里面被打开 但从外面就很容易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么问题来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是什么角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恶魔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么说我防御力最高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来攻击本大爷试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只能上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我能定住对本大爷抱有敌意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是本大爷名字的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.66,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可为什么我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为你没有敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你很弱也没拿武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有了小尼 我真的一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果燐就这样死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我绝对不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从外面可以打开门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然可以 不过你就出不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是为了大家 我也必须救出燐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能死在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你会老实等着被骑士团杀掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 还有自杀这个选项哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能让大家救我的努力白费
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是再拔出这把剑 我会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.22,0:16:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次说不定真的会伤到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真的应该去死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还什么忙都没帮上 就要死掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到头来 连跟大家和好都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我到底是为什么被救下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.94,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老头子 为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诗惠美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我来救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雾隐老师把事情都告诉我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们会和你一起战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快点从这里出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我没信心能控制住火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一直觉得可以靠气势来解决一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但这好像行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死了比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不准再说这种话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不用懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别这样 别这样笑着疏远我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我很想帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你走吧 我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一点都不烫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只想着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从没认真关注过燐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样还算什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}笨 笨蛋 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.74,0:19:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看 我根本就没有被烧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你保护了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不怕我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奥村同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家都是来救我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我不想让你死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要知道你没有危险 我就会跟你和好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}子猫丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我先声明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只是听从了雾隐老师的指示罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可是很不想来的 表扬我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕… 同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和老爸吵架的事确实是我不够冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说得没错 仅限和老爸吵架的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是战斗要用的吧 拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我 我才是 打了你对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我带你去金刚深山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之后要怎样随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.65,0:20:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要用我的方式战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然身为撒旦之子的事实无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我一定会把火焰控制好给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那种事情怎样都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我之所以不能原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是因为你把这些事全都闷在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么都不跟我们说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要我怎么相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道只有我一个人觉得我们是同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不是的 我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 就是因为这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你生气就只是因为这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这原因真新颖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}志摩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}胜吕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.28,0:21:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}舞台和演员终于齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 就让我尽情欣赏这场战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}目标是洛北的金刚深山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去打倒不净王
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.99,0:22:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只能用接下来的行动证明自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:05.34,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第八集 父子相传
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.77,0:24:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是自愿选择现在这条路的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟爸爸和哥哥无关
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
